==English==
===Etymology===
From Latin '''[[manualis|manuālis]]''', adjectival form of '''[[manus]]''' ''hand'', and derived term '''[[manuale|manuāle]]''' ''handbook'', ''manual''.

===Pronunciation===
{| border=1 cellpadding=5
